-- Norges Bank holds 2.048 pct stake in Ansaldo STS -Consob
-- By Agnieszka Flak
-- Mon Dec 29, 2014 07:43AM EST
-- None



MILAN, Dec 29 (Reuters) - Norges Bank has a 2.048 percent stake in Italian rail technology group Ansaldo STS <STS.MI>, data from market watchdog Consob showed on Monday.

Ansaldo STS is a unit of Finmeccanica <SIFI.MI> and is one of the subsidiaries the Italian defense and aerospace group has put up for sale to slim down and focus its operations.